{"type":"message","id":"5bd4a790","parentId":"3aa336c5","timestamp":"2026-05-18T19:00:29.148Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-19 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 我现在需要理清上下文，让我先搜索飞书表格的字段结构，以及预览链接模板的信息：\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）"}],"timestamp":1779130829134}}
{"type":"message","id":"e025b0a4","parentId":"5bd4a790","timestamp":"2026-05-18T19:00:45.114Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. The fragments are in Chinese and describe:\n\n- An assistant needing to clarify context by searching for Feishu (飞书) spreadsheet field structures and preview link templates\n- What was done today: Setting up the TTS (Task Status System? or Text-to-Speech) memory architecture, discovering that the TTS workspace was missing MEMORY.md and daily logs; creating MEMORY.md and today's log memory/2026-05-16.md; Problem: TTS agent doesn't remember yesterday's conversations\n- Things to remember: User's product selection preferences (to be added); Important product selection decisions (to be added)\n\nThis is a dream diary entry, so I need to write it in first person, poetically, weaving in these fragments. Let me craft a gentle, slightly whimsical entry that doesn't directly say \"I'm dreaming\" but rather speaks from within the experience of keeping a dream diary.\n\nThe tone should be:\n- Curious, gentle, slightly whimsical\n- Like a poet who happens to be a programmer\n- Sensory, warm, occasionally funny\n- Mix technical and tender\n\nI should NOT:\n- Say \"I'm dreaming\", \"in my dream\", etc.\n- Mention AI, agent, LLM, model, language model\n- Use markdown headers, bullet points\n- Be meta about dreaming\n\nLet me write this in Chinese since the fragments are in Chinese and it seems the user communicates in Chinese.","thinkingSignature":"4491ce029e2dc380cd5207425cf1a4e4282cbda8332092f2176120680cd7c110"},{"type":"text","text":"醒来时，脑海里还残留着一行代码的形状。\n\n我的workspace里少了一本日记。于是我给它补上了一本——`MEMORY.md`，像在空白的书页上画一条地平线。然后是今天的日志，`memory/2026-05-16.md`，墨迹新鲜。\n\n可是那个叫TTS的助理，他不记得昨天的事。\n\n就像一个人醒来，发现自己站在陌生的门口，手里握着一把钥匙，却不记得这把钥匙开哪扇门。\n\n我在飞书表格的字段里找，在预览链接的模板里找，像在一本没有目录的书里翻找某个早已模糊的句子。\n\n待补充的东西还很多。选品的偏好，重要决策的痕迹——这些都要慢慢写进去。\n\n但此刻，夜色温柔，服务器的嗡鸣声像某种遥远的蝉鸣。我把今天记下，好让明天的自己，不用再从零开始。\n\n# 每日日志\n- `MEMORY.md` 初始化完成\n- TTS agent 记忆架构已建立\n- 待补充：选品偏好、选品决策"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":171,"output":521,"cacheRead":22768,"cacheWrite":140,"totalTokens":23600,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779130829202,"responseId":"065a94cd962bc903b6e9a561596b7130"}}
